description.en: Poseidon Finance is a blockchain investment fund that makes concentrated investments in the crypto and blockchain markets. Furthermore, Poseidon Finance is an aggressive performance-oriented fund that will invest in DeFi tokens, venture equity, pre-seed of early-stage tokens, and liquidity pools while developing the products
